anceOf(StandardEnvironment.class);\n            assertThat(environment.getActiveProfiles()).containsExactly(\"converted\");\n            assertThat(environment.getProperty(\"sample.value\")).isEqualTo(\"from-argument\");\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class StandardEnvironmentContextFactory implements ApplicationContextFactory {\n\n        @Override\n        public Class<? extends ConfigurableEnvironment> getEnvironmentType(WebApplicationType webApplicationType) {\n            return StandardEnvironment.class;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public ConfigurableApplicationContext create(WebApplicationType webApplicationType) {\n            return new AnnotationConfigApplicationContext();\n        }\n\n    }\n\n    @SpringBootConfiguration(proxyBeanMethods = false)\n    public static class TestApplication {\n\n    }\n\n}\n"}
