[assistant] Added a dedicated test for `org.springframework.boot.EnvironmentConverter`:
[assistant] 
[assistant] - `tests/src/org.springframework.boot/spring-boot/4.0.2/src/test/java/org_springframework_boot/spring_boot/EnvironmentConverterTest.java`
